{"tid":1554793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵指閉路電視涉及市民資料　需慎重考慮","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:22:23.000Z","uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f2a80cf810a7398dbb6982918dadc1321a7847","tid":1554793,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆及港鐵高層視察受破壞的港鐵站。港鐵指，正和政府部門研究能否公開831太子站的閉路電視片段，但由於涉及其他市民的資料，需慎重考慮。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成：「閉路電視內的記錄很多牽涉其他人的資料，大家放心，我知道大家的關注，所以在這方面都要思考好，但大家最近的關心不需關心、擔心，因為我們的記錄一定會保留起碼三年，這方面大家可繼續討論。」<br />\n<br />\n陳帆：「香港鐵路是香港人的鐵路，很重要的是，它每天服務五百四十萬人，是香港公共交通重要的持份者。損壞鐵路設施，即是損壞香港市民享用有效率的公共服務。我希望參與破壞設施的暴亂人士尊重香港人出行的自由和權利。」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362159&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=500f91bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362159&h=c72b8984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=362159</a>"},{"pid":"e3b6ca25beedb7613e2b50ae9ab60539d585548c","tid":1554793,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ac26d32cf86b8980fdb859494f1ca2f1ee0ab2","tid":1554793,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"死都唔公開，send上大陸改梗内容！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281981598a96c19fba2a2e7869afb7e0849ac98c","tid":1554793,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:17:39.000Z",